Euro Group Says Greek Loan Payment in First Half of November

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-21T18:16:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/euro-group-says-greek-loan-payment-in-first-half-of-november.html
Euro-area finance chiefs said a
sixth aid payment to  Greece  “is expected to take place in the
first half of November, pending the approval by the board of the
International Monetary Fund,” according to a statement posted
on the euro group’s website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
